ation, die quer zu vorgegebenen Bahnen liegt.  afunded by Universität Kassel  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aArbeit. 4aAusbildung. 4aBerufsabschluss. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aBildungssoziologie. 4aBiografische Forschung. 4aLebenslanges Lernen. 4aPädagogik. 4aQualifikation. 4aSoziologie. 4aVerwaltung. 4aWeiterbildung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh  aAdministration.  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aFurther Education.  aLifelong Learning.  aPedagogy.  aProfessional Qualification.  aQualification.  aSociology of Education.  aSociology.  aTraning.  aWork.2 aUniversität Kassel efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2022z9783110994520oZDB-23-DSL40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839462539?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839462539zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839462539/original  a978-3-11-076700-1 DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSLb2022  aZDB-23-GOA